            "the news is all about her", "she uses the whole loaf of bread", "the noodles run away", "she falls through the ice",
            "the king surrenders", "she's the only one not laughing", "the sun gets jealous", "they ask for her autograph",
            "it takes a team of people", "the pencil breaks", "the cake falls", "the music is just her footsteps",
            "the fish jump out of the water", "the trail ends", "the horse needs a chiropractor", "the oven quits",
            "the drawbridge collapses", "the comedian asks for her material", "the balls hide", "the belt melts",
            "the lettuce wilts", "the spring gives up"
